title: BNP Multiracial Britain. The Truth. .wmv
description:
Witness the truth about Blairs failed multi-cultural Britain.

An interview between Nick Cass, Clr. Angela Clarke and a white resident who has been on the receiving end of a campaign of racial harassment by young Muslim thugs. A distressing story which includes threat of eviction by the landlord, death threats and physical assaults. An everyday story of life for white folks in multi-cultural Britain.

(from bnp.org.uk)
